data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! With 80 ft of waterfront and just one bridge away from the Gulf of Mexico you are bound to fall in love. This 4-bed, 3-bath home offers 2,730 sq ft of comfort and luxury. The custom saltwater pool, built after 2016, and lanai create a contemporary outdoor space. Enjoy sunsets, wildlife, and a fire pit by the water. Inside, travertine floors welcome you, with two water view living areas. The spacious kitchen with granite countertops overlooks the water. Two master bedrooms with ensuite and walk-in closets provide ultimate luxury. Privacy is ensured with a well-equipped with a $10,000 RO Rainsoft system. Updates include a new seawall, roof, and accordion hurricane shutters. Conveniently situated in between North Port and Englewood, you have endless shopping, restaurants and beaches all within a short drive. This truly is the perfect home in the perfect location! Don't miss the opportunity to own this extraordinary waterfront retreat.
